                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7111" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0219</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8911 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">危则思变：民营企业苏博建材的风险管理探索之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Thinking of change in case of danger: the road of risk management exploration of private enterprise Subo building materials</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王德发，代文，赵欣欣，王雪松，陈艺苹</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉苏博新型建材有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险管理；内部控制；COSO-ERM</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Risk management; Internal control ; Coso-erm</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新冠疫情的爆发，对国内的各行各业均造成了冲击，我国的基建行业无疑也在疫情中受到了巨大影响。如何化解并平稳度过这次风浪？如何识别疫情下企业经营过程中的风险并且及时应对？这是几乎所有企业在公司治理和风险管理方面的“燃眉之急”。本案例选取湖北省外加剂龙头企业苏博建材为描述对象，利用2017版的COSO-ERM企业全面风险管理框架对苏博建材开展全面的风险管理排查，然后就疫情下民营企业应该如何识别经营过程中存在的风险和如何针对已有风险作出应对措施讨论和探究。通过本案例的学习，可以帮助学习者了解疫情下企业在风险管理、内部控制及公司治理等方面存在的问题，引发学习者进行理性的分析与思考，也为同类企业疫情背景下的风险管理提供参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The outbreak of COVID-19 epidemic has impacted all walks of life in China, and China&#39;s infrastructure industry has undoubtedly been greatly affected by the epidemic. How to resolve and weather this storm smoothly? How to identify the risks in the business process under the epidemic situation and deal with them in time? This is the &quot;urgent need&quot; of almost all enterprises in corporate governance and risk management. In this case, Subo Building Materials, a leading admixture enterprise in Hubei Province, is selected as the description object, and the COSO-ERM Enterprise Comprehensive Risk Management Framework (2017 edition) is used to conduct a comprehensive risk management investigation on Subo Building Materials. Then, how to identify the risks existing in the business process and how to take countermeasures against the existing risks under the epidemic situation are discussed and explored. Through the study of this case, it can help learners understand the problems existing in risk management, internal control and financial strategy of enterprises under the epidemic situation, arouse learners&#39; rational analysis and thinking, and provide reference value for risk management of similar enterprises under the epidemic situation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制》、《风险管理》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险管理的概念和实行风险管理的必要性；组织架构的类型及其各自优缺点和如何结合具体公司对组织架构进行完善；企业文化的意义和其必要性；COSO-ERM (2017)风险管理框架；如何构建企业全面风险管理体系</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
